], and made available for our studies through the University of South Alabama Center for Lung Biology Cell Culture Core. Low passage number cells (<15) were routinely cultured in DMEM high glucose medium (Invitrogen) containing 10% fetal bovine serum (DMEM/FBS) and grown at 37 °C, (5% CO

